data.description: Adorable cottage style 3 bedroom home in PNGISD, in a great central location that has not flooded, per seller. This is an ideal new home or investment property. This updated & charming home has a big fenced in backyard that you & your pets can enjoy for outdoor fun and festivities year round. The fresh exterior colors give it a quaint & inviting curb appeal. Fresh grey & white interior paint & the wood look vinyl plank flooring provide a neutral canvas to make it your own. Plenty of kitchen counter space, cabinet storage, plus a coordinating white gas cooktop and vent a hood. Updated brushed nickel hardware on the doors & bathroom fixtures. You will also have an updated bathroom vanity and light fixture. It is equipped with Central AC and heat and a gas water heater. And ceiling fans are always a plus to use year round, here in SETX. One car attached garage to park a vehicle or store your extras in. It also has a washer and dryer hookup in the garage utility area for your convenience!
